The Shotgun OHV Area offers 24 miles of year-round trails for Class I, II, and III vehicles. The riding area consists of logging roads and dirt trails that run through forests and creeks. The area is located east of Springfield, Oregon.

The Millican Valley Off-Highway Vehicle (OHV) Trail System consists of lands southwest of Prineville, Oregon along George Millican Road, extending south of Highway 20. Trails and play areas are provided for Class I, II, and III off-highway vehicles (OHVs)
